	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In other words, the extra 50 or so lines happen between the end of the picture and NMI. So to get the most out of a Dendy's vblank time, you need to turn rendering off early using sprite 0, DMC IRQ, or a mapper IRQ.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
